column5: This cute little guy was sent to me by Jack (Nanook). I can't imagine how vulnerable that poor little guy would be out in the wild.

yeah that picture has been floating around for about a year now each time I receive it, there is a different story about it and who has it  it is cool.. those red eyes make it look evil...don't you think
This poor little guy looks evil/terrestrial too.
Algonquin moose. Would be good camo in the snow anyway.
The story I got is that it was found at the side of the road last spring,no mother around. Zoo's were interested in  it but it went to a wildlife rehab. farm.  Thanks Roy !!
